# ğŸš— Garage Management System

A full-stack web application for managing a car garage, built with Flask, SQLAlchemy, and Jinja2 templates. Track clients, their cars, and service status in one centralized system.

## ğŸŒŸ Features

### Client Management
- âœ… Create, Read, Update, Delete (CRUD) clients
- âœ… Store client information (name, email, phone, ID number)
- âœ… View client details with associated cars
- âœ… Cascade delete protection (warns before deleting clients with cars)

### Car Management
- âœ… Full CRUD operations for cars
- âœ… Track car details (brand, model, year, plate number, color)
- âœ… Service status tracking (Pending, In Progress, Ready, Delivered)
- âœ… Link cars to owners (clients)
- âœ… Color picker for car color selection

### User Interface
- ğŸ“± Responsive design (mobile-friendly)
- ğŸ¨ Modern, clean interface with card-based layouts
- ğŸ” Detailed views for both cars and clients
- âš¡ Smooth transitions and hover effects
- ğŸ¯ Intuitive navigation

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Flask 3.1.2** - Web framework
- **SQLAlchemy 2.0.45** - ORM for database operations
- **Flask-SQLAlchemy 3.1.1** - Flask integration for SQLAlchemy
- **Flask-Migrate 4.1.0** - Database migrations
- **PostgreSQL** (Production) / **SQLite** (Development)

### Frontend
- **Jinja2 3.1.6** - Template engine
- **HTML5 & CSS3** - Structure and styling
- **Responsive Grid Layout** - Mobile-first design

### Deployment
- **Gunicorn 23.0.0** - WSGI HTTP server
- **Render** - Cloud platform (production deployment)

